description: Recently, Cameron Adams and Leo Forte joined forces and fought on the same team in a powerful tag team match and they got their asses kicked. They each blame the other for being the weak link and are jonesing to prove it. This aggressive grudge match takes place in Palm Springs during the dead of winter. Two big-dicked studs battling it out to show who has the skills and who was the weakest link in their tag team match. Winner owns the loser's ass and fucks it long and hard until he begs for mercy!
title: Cameron Adams vs Leo Forte
